snippet.title: Tulips & Windmills 🌷 - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
How did you end up here!?

Well, anyways, are you ready to collect some tulips at this simple but addicting clicker game? It's free! 

Hoi! Ensure your windmill runs consistently and your tulip fields are harvested. This clicker game will bring you closer to the iconic Dutch culture. Expect random events and make use of upgrades to increase your tulip wealth! Veel succes!

Launching February 5th, 2025 on Steam.
Wishlist now to not miss anything! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1883980/

Music by Vlad Krotov from Pixabay.

#steam #steamgame #TulipsWindmills
